          'No one can say "Jesus is Lord" except by the Holy Spirit, who awakens and sustains our faith (CCC 683, 687).',
          'Scripture reveals the Spirit through symbols: water, anointing, fire, cloud and light, the seal, and the dove (CCC 694-701).',
