          "John the Baptist, filled with the Spirit from the womb, completed the prophets' work of preparing a people for the Lord (CCC 717-720).",
          'In Mary, and above all in Christ Jesus, the Spirit\'s work in the fullness of time is revealed and accomplished (CCC 721-730).',
